Titus Welliver https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Titus_Welliver 0 Titus B. Welliver (born March 12, 1961) is an American actor. He is best known for his portrayals of the Man in Black on Lost, Silas Adams on Deadwood, Jimmy O’Phelan on Sons of Anarchy, and the title role in the television series Bosch.
